      <description>&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;What if your AI agent could not just write code, but also manage the entire git lifecycle automatically? That&amp;amp;rsquo;s exactly what issue #102 is addressing - and it&amp;amp;rsquo;s representing a significant leap forward in autonomous software development.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
